{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-doc-tsx","path":"/doc/providers/tencent/cli-reference/install","result":{"data":{"doc":{"id":"d1519f20-d7af-5abb-b3ff-51972161d97d","html":"<h3 id=\"环境准备\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87\" aria-label=\"环境准备 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>环境准备</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>安装 npm：前往 <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/\">Node.js 官网</a> 下载对应平台的安装程序（Node 8+ 版本）。</li>\n<li>安装完成后，执行 <code class=\"language-text\">npm -v</code> 确认是否安装成功。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"安装-cli\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-cli\" aria-label=\"安装 cli permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装 CLI</h3>\n<p>执行以下命令安装/更新 CLI ：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"># 安装 CLI\n$ npm install -g serverless</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"升级-cli\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7-cli\" aria-label=\"升级 cli permalink\" class=\"anchor b